lead_paragraph: Japan's shocking win over New Zealand and a tournament-ending injury to Sonny Bill Williams proved on the first day of Olympic men's rugby in 92 years what coaches have long been saying about the sevens format.

headline.print_headline: Japan Upset New Zealand, Williams Out in Rocky Rugby Return
